\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces LLM Sandbox architecture: the Input Probe captures the full request context; the Model Invoker runs isolated inference; the Safety Evaluator applies deterministic checks against the Safety Envelope; the Decision Emitter emits Go/No-Go. The \textit  {Fact Layer}\ layer enforces the No-Go decision, blocking the action from reaching actuators. The forensic ledger records every Sandbox event.}}{1}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
